children.value: Led and mentored 40+ junior engineers on computer science fundamentals, data structures/algorithms, software engineering best practices, modern full-stack web development technologies (including React, Redux, Node, Express), databases (including MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Cassandra), and app deployment technologies (including AWS EC2, S3, Docker, various load testing tools).
Performed code reviews, and acted as a technical expert during architecture/software design and implementation phases for over 100 projects.
Acted as first correspondence between students and staff ensuring clear and proper communication between both parties.
